I think that the belts should have one defence fight per year per belt.
For example
1. January WBC
2. April IBF
3. July WBO
4. October IBO
Any challenger should fight for one belt at a time, therefore to become unified you should fight and win 4 fights, to have all the belts not one fight for all.
Even if you have to fight the same opponent twice to get another belt so be it.
Not just have one fight and pick them all up, you have to work for each. Can someone tell me if they disagree or agree with this?
